! Single Block Transclusion

You can transclude a single block from another tiddler using `{{Title^blockId}}`:

<<wikitext-example-without-html src:"{{Block Level Links in WikiText^BlockLevelLinksID1}}">>

This will render only the block with that block ID, not the entire tiddler.

! Block-Level Backlinks

Use the `backlinks:blockid` filter suffix to find tiddlers linking to a specific block ID:

```
[{!!title}backlinks:blockid[BlockLevelLinksID1]]
```

Use the `blockids` filter to find which block IDs a source tiddler links to in a target:

```
[<sourceTiddler>blockids[TargetTitle]]
```